cs.SY, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE

The paper deals with Hamilton-Jacobi reachability analysis for control-affine systems, which is a topic related to control theory and robotics. Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also presents a machine learning approach for approximating the optimal controller, which falls under the scope of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves optimization and decision-making, which are relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
